{"tid":1913261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲「廁紙之亂」 報紙加印8頁「廁紙」應急！！","createTime":"2020-03-06T15:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T17:26:39.000Z","uid":209657,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ede22da70ba885144003f4cd87466534834e82e6","tid":1913261,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ESQSq2jUcAA3dLa?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FESQSq2jUcAA3dLa%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&h=56a71ba1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「廁紙之亂」近日在社交媒體上成為熱門話題，「#廁紙緊急狀態」（#ToiletPaperEmergency）、「#廁紙末日」（#ToiletPaperApocalypse）等標籤隨之興起。《北領地新聞報》3月4日率先向讀書預告會加印8頁「廁紙」，並公開的圖樣，讀者可以裁成「單層廁紙」使用。"},{"pid":"38e2a40cc8f30c4b6e7421bbc3d92a6621c289bd","tid":1913261,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:44:09.000Z","msg":"《北領地新聞報》編輯威廉斯（Matt Williams）向《衛報》澳洲版表示，特別版銷情很好，顯然不是劣質的版本。他說：「我們的報章以了解讀者需要而聞名於世，北領地人目前對廁紙有極大需求，所以我們要供應他們所需。」<br />\n<br />\n澳洲大型超級市場科爾斯（Coles）和伍爾沃思（Woolworths）有大量顧客搶購廁紙和搓手液，很多分店的貨架空空如也，超市被迫限購廁紙。布里斯班（Brisbane）一架載有廁紙的貨車3月4日引擎爆炸釀成火災，廁紙雖然未受影響，但亦引起市民恐慌，擔心廁紙供應短缺。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ESOya4LUcAIFssT?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FESOya4LUcAIFssT%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dsmall&h=03f9bc96&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"036f881ced8849da63a00e47bea570e79375b37b","tid":1913261,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:44:44.000Z","msg":"屙屎之亂解決辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n脫離支那是是香港唯一出路，但絕不能直接獨立，必須先經英美託管一段時間再經公投獨立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913061</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6a2d30f334a7ab4159dc6b3739d4f53c3adcedd0","tid":1913261,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:45:21.000Z","msg":"#ToiletPaperApocalypse<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e61ae1d06d92a7657dd9722.jpg/a9LIYUJe5gxVx7Ag9QYwHMrrMRP8Cwa4PhupSj4bqUo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e61ae1d06d92a7657dd9722.jpg%2Fa9LIYUJe5gxVx7Ag9QYwHMrrMRP8Cwa4PhupSj4bqUo&h=cc10b8e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4006a820dad9cd75d0f1526ab8e937f580e1a235","tid":1913261,"uid":34765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:45:46.000Z","msg":"點解搶廁紙？<br />\n見之前香港搶就跟住搶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"956e4ebd5cb1c18870af2158aef57e83b36585fd","tid":1913261,"uid":256495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:45:50.000Z","msg":"香港人走在最前<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3d81a6db714660a06878db99f58c31096760da5","tid":1913261,"uid":51469,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:46:17.000Z","msg":"Failed states<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},